30
00:01:21,439 --> 00:01:21,680
[UNKNOWN] Nula.

31
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:23,359
[SPEAKER_01] Pitanje drugo.

32
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:25,280
[SPEAKER_00] Kaj si me to odmah pitao, to si bar trebao na kraju.

33
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:26,079
